<!DOCTYPE qhelp SYSTEM "qhelp.dtd">
<qhelp>
  <overview>
    <p>Privileged TanStack server functions must run inside the authenticated or mutation context wrapper.</p>
  </overview>
  <recommendation>
    <p>Route non-public server functions through <code>runProtected</code>, <code>runMutation</code>, <code>withProtectedContext</code>, or <code>withProtectedMutation</code>.</p>
  </recommendation>
</qhelp>
